title: 2019 Week 12 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 12 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview each of the upcoming week 12 games with their snake draft. There are some big matchups in week 12 including Seahawks Eagles (5:14), Cowboys at Patriots (11:46) and Green Bay at the 49ers (1:06:02) .

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
